Package ScreenForms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InterfaceAEW
    Interface for Add Element Window functionality Defines methods for adding rows to tables
    InterfaceDEW
    Interface for Delete Element Window functionality Defines methods for deleting rows from tables
    InterfaceEEW
    Interface for Edit Element Window functionality Defines methods for editing existing table rows
    InterfaceIOW
    Interface for Input Output Window functionality Defines common methods for all input/output dialog windows
    InterfaceMW
    Interface for Main Window functionality Defines methods for the main application window operations
    InterfacePW
    Interface for Printer Window functionality Defines methods for printer-related operations
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddElementWindow
    Window for adding new rows to the table User can enter data for a new dog entry
    DeleteElementWindow
    Window for deleting rows from the table User can select a row to remove from the data
    EditElementWindow
    Window for editing existing rows in the table User can select a row and change its data
    InputOutputWindow
    Base class for all input and output windows in the application Provides common functionality for dialogs that get user input and show messages to the user
    MainWindow
    Main window class for the Dog Festival application Handles GUI creation and user interface components
    PrinterWindow
    Window for displaying printer error messages Shows a dialog when printer is not available
